, ensuring that every patient receives the best possible care.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-105_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multiracial-team-of-doctors-having-morning-breefin-2023-11-27-04-59-42-utc.jpg?v=1709043897" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multiracial-team-of-doctors-having-morning-breefin-2023-11-27-04-59-42-utc.jpg?v=1709043897 1536w" width="2000" height="1125" alt="Professional Body Recommendations in Healthcare: Learn with ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Professional Body Recommendations in Healthcare: Learn with ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-106_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-107_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by  Prostock-studio via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a631" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-uojGG hMqLeX pf-109_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ilfuhL bpQaoh"><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-110_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-111_"><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-112_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/dr-richard-dune-blog" target="_blank"></a>In the complex world of healthcare, clinical governance pillars have emerged as a pivotal strategy for ensuring excellence in patient care. Rooted in accountability, this framework guides healthcare organisations in the UK and beyond, enabling them to navigate the multifaceted challenges of delivering health services. Understanding the pillars of clinical governance is essential for any healthcare professional committed t